        <font color="midnightblue" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> The Companions folks (err, folk - one guy 4 boxing!) were pleasant enough once we got up there, and actually called out loots for the taking frequently.  Crazi ended up with not one but two Iksar warrior bracers that way, and I think that bard and chanty loot was also obtained from Companions by our party.</P><P>I'd love to spend more time on the second floor as it is largely new territory for us...plus, the possibility of uber Paladin drops there pique my interest!</P><P><b>Tenuvil Bravesteel</b><BR>56th level Paladin of Mithaniel Marr<BR>Lord of Events - LOA-EQ</P><P><i>"I swear--by my life and my love of it--that I will never live for the sake of another man, nor ask another man to live for mine." - John Galt</i><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
